    "• Avoid short-answer questions or questions that query basic, elementary knowledge that is easily found on the internet.",
    "In addition to these suggestions, we considered other means by which LLM-methods could be circumvented or detected if used by students for generation of answers.",
    "However, upon further discussion we identified some means that each of these could be overcome (listed below):",
    "• For essay questions, require students to refer to multiple course materials, such as lecture slides.",
    "o This strategy may be countered by students copy/pasting the relevant course material text into ChatGPT, or by using a programming script to feed course slides as background for the question into the OpenAI API."
